html.body: Upon ligand-receptor recognition, DAP12 is phosphorylated by Lymphocyte-specific protein tyrosine kinase (Lck) and FYN oncogene related to SRC, FGR and YES (Fyn) [5]. These phosphorylation events result in recruitment of SYK family kinases such as Spleen tyrosine kinase (Syk) and Zeta-chain associated protein kinase 70kDa (ZAP70)
DAP12 probably activates SHC (Src homology 2 domain containing) transforming protein 1 (Shc) via ZAP70
or NKp46-associated FcR, and CD3chain-dependentactivation of Syk/ZAP70/PI3K signalin
